    • Uses of ConnectionConfiguration in com.genesyslab.platform.commons.connection.configuration

      Classes in com.genesyslab.platform.commons.connection.configuration that implement ConnectionConfiguration 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  AbstractConnectionConfiguration
      AbstractConnectionConfiguration is an abstract class which implements common methods assuming that real container can hold only string values.
      class  KeyValueConfiguration
      The implementation of ConnectionConfiguration interface, which contains all values in KeyValueCollection.
      class  ManagedConfiguration
      Managed configuration is wrapper for ConnectionConfiguration.
      class  PropertyConfiguration
      The implementation of ConnectionConfiguration interface, which contains all values in java.util.Properties.
